I make this dish often as it is quick and easy. I always follow the recipe to a "T". For the cook who was having problems with the cream curdling, this was because of the lower fat content in the lighter cream, it is less stable than full fat cream particularly when cooked with alcohol and this is why it curdled. Light cream does not hold up well when cooked.

