Rating: 4
I now make this dish quite often, and we love it. A couple suggestions/pointers, though: It's safe to substitute the butter with some extra olive oil, but not the cream. Low-fat dairy ruins the sauce. As always, use a wine you'd be happy to drink, the drier the better. We like a good sauvignon blanc over the several other varietals we've tried. Use the sweet sausage -- hot destroys the balance.

