This recipe is "Haute Hamburger Helper!" I offer an alternative version (from cheap college days) Brown 1/2 pound of hamburger or sausage. Mix with 1 prepare package of Kraft macaroni & cheese and 1 drained can of tomatoes. Voila! 80% of the taste - 20% of the effort.

